  "texts": [
    "The backbone, neck, and head comprise the three essential structural components of the YOLO series of models.",
    "The original architercture of Yolov5 is shown in Fig. 3.",
    "Darknet is used by YOLOv5 as the backbone to extract features from photos composed of cross-stage partial networks.",
    "In the YOLOv5 neck, the features are aggregated using a feature pyramid network created by PANet, which is then sent to the head for prediction.",
    "Concerning object detection, the YOLOv5 head has layers that produce predictions from anchor boxes."
  ],
